{"tid":1197723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港社會工作者總工會 呼籲612集體請假 準備罷工】","createTime":"2019-06-10T05:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T05:26:02.000Z","uid":5253,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"36cb135bd442c65e9816e4a3d96d62f2102eab6f","tid":1197723,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b6nBU3b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb6nBU3b.png&h=7704cc55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨日103萬香港人上街，清楚表達反對送中條例的訴求，可惜政府漠視民意，並即晚發出聲明，表示法案如期於6月12日進行二讀。今天林鄭仍然執迷不悟，我們感到強烈憤怒，各行各業正蘊釀以罷工罷課罷市作進一步的抗爭！社總呼籲非緊急服務的同工於6月12日集體請假，到立法會外聲援會議廳中的民主派議員，與保皇黨決戰。<br />\n<br />\n我們與社福界緊密商討，做好準備，部署下一步行動。社總呼籲同工留意社總公佈，準備隨時升級行動，包括罷工！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/165937923461968/posts/2199363436786063?s=1774405881&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F165937923461968%2Fposts%2F2199363436786063%3Fs%3D1774405881%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QYvF2KwMlxx6JcZ5CCC9GHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=8d742aff\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/165937923461968/posts/2199363436786063?s=1774405881&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"da28b221a99e77793865a8070b008cf440bce3ff","tid":1197723,"uid":93043,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:07:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da40b15242e6d581d82ef15338c702b8599cd81a","tid":1197723,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69bedb3e8275f618325106bcd7c7f46a3733f92f","tid":1197723,"uid":102880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:26:02.000Z","msg":"社工要俾返d 應有既風骨出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}